OL,7,FMPs are urging the government to take
OL,8,Faction over a controversial pregnancy
OL,9,Fdrug which has links to cancer, as ITV
OL,10,FNews Social Affairs Editor Sarah
OL,11,FCorker reports
OL,13,FA group of more than 30 MPs has
OL,14,Fwritten a letter to the Health
OL,15,FSecretary urging him to take action
OL,16,Fover a controversial drug given to
OL,17,Fpregnant women, following an ITV News
OL,18,Finvestigation.
