OL,3,CMPs urge health secretary to take
OL,4,Caction over cancer-linked pregnancy
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FStilbestrol, also known as DES, was
OL,8,Fprescribed to an estimated 300,000
OL,9,Fwomen to prevent miscarriage and stop
OL,10,Fbreast milk until the late 1970s, when
OL,11,Fit was linked to an aggressive type of
OL,12,Fcancer.
OL,14,FIf the drug was taken by women who
OL,15,Fwere pregnant, the harm could have
OL,16,Fbeen passed down to their children.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
