OL,4,Caction over cancer-linked pregnancy
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FITV News has been contacted by
OL,8,Fhundreds of women who say their health
OL,9,Fhas been damaged by DES - and last
OL,10,Fweek we revealed that it was still
OL,11,Fbeing prescribed to women on the NHS
OL,12,Fnearly a decade after it should have
OL,13,Fbeen banned.
OL,15,FNow MPs are calling on the government
OL,16,Fto take action and save lives.
