OL,7,FThe letter, coordinated by Bournemouth
OL,8,FMP Jessica Toale, urges Wes Streeting
OL,9,Fto formally apologise to victims of
OL,10,Fthe medical scandal and to commit to
OL,11,Fenhanced cancer screenings for those
OL,12,Fexposed.
OL,14,FWhat are MPs calling for?
OL,16,FJessica Toale wrote the letter after
OL,17,Fhearing her constituent Jan Hall's
OL,18,Fstory on ITV News.
