OL,7,FJan, 75, from Bournemouth, believes
OL,8,Fher mother Rita was prescribed DES
OL,9,Fduring three pregnancies and that
OL,10,Fexposure contributed to her death,
OL,11,Faged 32, from breast cancer in 1951,
OL,12,Fwhen Jan was a toddler.
OL,14,F"Frankly it's shocking that we don't
OL,15,Fknow how many women and families have
OL,16,Fbeen affected by this, so we really
OL,17,Fneed to do some work to raise
OL,18,Fawareness and to make sure we have the
OL,19,Fprotocols in place to screen people."
