OL,7,FJessica Toale MP explains why she is
OL,8,Fcalling for action
OL,10,FThe legacy of this drug has been
OL,11,Fdevastating, with the harmful effects
OL,12,Fnot limited to the women who were
OL,13,Fprescribed DES.
OL,15,FMedical research suggests it extends
OL,16,Facross generations, affecting their
OL,17,Fdaughters who have an increased risk
OL,18,Fof rare types of cancer and fertility
OL,19,Fproblems.
