OL,7,FITV News has spoken to one woman from
OL,8,FChichester who was exposed to the drug
OL,9,Fwhile her mother was pregnant and was
OL,10,Fforced to have a hysterectomy when she
OL,11,Fwas just nine-years-old and nearly
OL,12,Fdied from complications.
OL,14,F54-year-old Charly Laurence was just a
OL,15,Fchild when she was diagnosed with
OL,16,Fcervical cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
