OL,7,FDoctors said it was linked to the now
OL,8,Fbanned drug that her mother had been
OL,9,Fgiven whilst pregnant. She'd had
OL,10,Fmultiple miscarriages and was given
OL,11,FDES for prolonged periods of time.
OL,13,FCharly first started developing
OL,14,Fsymptoms when she was seven. Her
OL,15,Fmother took her to her original
OL,16,Fgynaecologist, who found the cancer
OL,17,Fafter a number of invasive
OL,18,Fexaminations.
