OL,12,FOver the next two years of Charly's
OL,13,Flife, she was subjected to countless
OL,14,Fprocedures and spent more time at
OL,15,Fhospital than she did at home.
OL,17,F"I remember them saying you are going
OL,18,Fto have an operation - unfortunately
OL,19,Fyou won't be able to have any babies,
OL,20,Fbut you can adopt when you are older,"
OL,21,FCharly told us.
