OL,7,F"I certainly understood the concept of
OL,8,Fnot being able to have a baby.
OL,10,F"I remember crying a lot as a child.
OL,11,FThey just kept reminding me that I was
OL,12,Fstill alive and I wasn't going to die
OL,13,Fof the cancer."
OL,15,FShe recently obtained her medical
OL,16,Ffiles, which show doctors in the UK
OL,17,Fwere even writing to scientists in the
OL,18,FUS about her condition.
