OL,7,FCharly believes she is at a higher
OL,8,Frisk of developing certain types of
OL,9,Fcancer and her mission now is calling
OL,10,Ffor more screening for women like her.
OL,12,FBut despite everything, she has defied
OL,13,Fthe odds and has gone on to have twin
OL,14,Fdaughters, through surrogacy.
OL,15,FTogether, the family wants to raise
OL,16,Fawareness of the impact of DES and
OL,17,Fmake sure others exposed to it get the
