OL,7,FWhat is DES?JDES, also known as
OL,8,FStilbrestrol, was prescribed on the
OL,9,FNHS to prevent miscarriage and to stop
OL,10,Fbreast milk production from 1939 until
OL,11,Fthe late 1970s.
OL,13,FIt was marketed as a 'wonder drug' and
OL,14,Fcontained a synthetic form of female
OL,15,Fhormone oestrogen. It has become one
OL,16,Fof the biggest drug disasters in the
OL,17,FNHS's history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
