OL,7,FThe UK government claimed that doctors
OL,8,Fwere told in 1973 to stop prescribing
OL,9,FDES for pre-menopausal women, however
OL,10,FITV News has found dozens of women who
OL,11,Fwere given the drug as late as 1980.
OL,13,FOther countries around the world, such
OL,14,Fas the United States, banned the drug
OL,15,Fin the 1970s as scientific studies
OL,16,Flinked the use of DES with breast,
OL,17,Fcervical, and vaginal cancers.
OL,19,FIn the UK, health authorities failed
OL,20,Fto do the same.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
