OL,7,FEarlier this month, the Health
OL,8,FSecretary said the government is
OL,9,Fconsidering enhanced cancer screening
OL,10,Ffor those impacted by the use of
OL,11,FStilbestrol, also known as DES, and
OL,12,Fhas vowed to "look seriously at these
OL,13,Fallegations".
OL,15,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "Our sympathies are
OL,17,Fwith anyone harmed by the historic use
OL,18,Fof Diethylstilboestrol (DES).
