OL,7,F"The Secretary of State has been clear
OL,8,Fhe will look seriously at these
OL,9,Fallegations, and the government will
OL,10,Fcontinue to consider enhanced
OL,11,Fscreening for those impacted by the
OL,12,Fuse of this drug."
OL,14,FThe Patient Safety Commissioner,
OL,15,FHenrietta Hughes, has welcomed the
OL,16,FHealth Secretary's views into the
OL,17,F"medication scandal" and is calling
OL,18,Ffor more support for those exposed to
OL,19,Fthe drug during pregnancy.
